reviewText: This video is a presentation of Sartre by means of third party commentaries and with sections of Sartre explaining himself. First it is in French, but if one gets past that the material is expansive but can be confusing. It moves back and forth from and to Sartre and the explanations are more current whereas the Sartre clips are towards the end of his life. If one wants to hear Sartre himself, there is enough here to cover it. It is however a somewhat uneven combination of commentary and the philosopher.
